---
title: Add App distribution with Bitrise
menu:
  tutorials-main:
    weight: 17

---
This tutorial describes how you can link Firebase App distribution to Bitrise Workflow 



Before you start, make sure you are signed in to your Firebase account on your computer. 

1. Install Firebase CLI ("https://firebase.google.com/docs/cli") for Mac OS || Linux Systeme

```bash 
curl -sL https://firebase.tools | bash
```
2. Once it is installed, fire up following command 

```bash 
firebase login:ci
```
You will have this format 1/sqdqsPdqh454....

3. no need to add Service Credentials File if you dont use it 

4. Add You App Path (Ipa or Apk) 
PS: sometimes you need to add full Archive path 

5. You need to add your testers group that you addede in App distribution under Firebase 

